               <p>JOHN CLOUGH sworn. - I am a <rs id="t18030420-41-viclabel221" type="occupation">merchant</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030420-41-victim423 t18030420-41-viclabel221"></join>: On Saturday last, about three o'clock, in <placeName id="t18030420-41-crimeloc222">Gracechurch-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18030420-41-crimeloc222" type="placeName" value="Gracechurch-street"></interp>
